<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>我的文档站点</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./css/style.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/highlight.js/11.8.0/styles/github.min.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <!-- 侧边栏导航 -->
        <nav class="sidebar">
            <div class="logo">
                <h1>📚 我的文档</h1>
            </div>
            <ul class="nav-menu">
                <li><a href="#" onclick="loadPage('docs/README.md')">🏠 首页</a></li>
                <li><a href="#" onclick="loadPage('docs/guide/index.md')">📖 指南</a></li>
                <li><a href="#" onclick="loadPage('docs/api/index.md')">🔧 API</a></li>
                <li><a href="#" onclick="loadPage('docs/guide/install.md')">⚡ 安装</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>

        <!-- 主内容区 -->
        <main class="content">
            <div class="content-header">
                <h1>欢迎访问我的文档</h1>
                <p>一个简单的静态文档站点</p>
            </div>
            <div id="content" class="markdown-body">
                <!-- 内容将通过JavaScript动态加载 -->
                <p>请从左侧导航选择要查看的文档。</p>
            </div>
        </main>
    </div>

    <!-- 脚本 -->
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/marked/marked.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/highlight.js/11.8.0/highlight.min.js"></script>
    <script src="./js/main.js"></script>
</body>
</html>